	   <tr><td colspan=2>Well, when I was 28 I hunted in the Southern Plains of Karana, killing gnolls at the spires. You could *maybe* solo the left-most spire, because it has a slower spawn rate. I just grouped, and when I hit 29 and 30 I hunted there because of new spells, and I soloed the middle spire. They have decent loot, and lots of Fine Steel weapons, and save the scrolls you get cause at least one person will be asking people to sell them to them. Although Magicians don't get a new DD at 29, you still can do fine.<br>&nbsp;<br>Meltem Elestorm 55 Magician, Heroic Intervention<br>Mithaniel Marr<br></td></tr>
