	   <tr><td colspan=2>You can also give your pets rusty two-handed scythes, which let them hit for 20, and are VERY cheap. Just go to sister island (the first stop between freeport and butcherblock), and buy some off of the merchant. Also, while I am at it, there are sisters that roam the island that are levels 7 -13. They ALL carry rusty two handed scythes and if you don't mind losing faction with the elves, you can kill them and take their scythes. Be careful thouhh, becuase they assist.<br><br>Also, on the island are level 25 sisters. One ont he dock of the island and one near a tree that is near the dock of the island. If you are level 24, you can successfully hunt one of them, and if you are level 29-34, you can stand at the end of the dock, and kill both of them, without the other one assisting.<br><br>Also ont he island are 3 dwarfs. Two are level 24 and one is level 25. These guys make excellent hunting for people that are levels 24-33 and they only drop your faction with a small sect of the dwarves in kaladim that you won't ever even need to interact with. With the expansions out this place is probably not being used as effently as it should, so I suggest going here if you need a place to hunt.<br><br>Former Addict of Everquest.<br><br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
