	   <tr><td colspan=2>Lake of Ill Omen is a great place to hunt, but it can get rather crowded. Personally, I liked Antonica when I played Everquest. At your levels a great spot besides Lake of Ill Omen is Lake Rathe, just south of southern karana on Antonica. In this zone there is a tower with 3 level 16-20 birds that repop every 6 minutes. They are easier than the regular mobs of their level. You guys would do great there.<br><br>Have fun everyone, keep the memory of EQ alive for me.<br><br>tim_gerber@yahoo.com for questions and comments<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
